data.name: test
data.script: function testFn(context) {const $ = context.jQuery;const submissions = $('.athing').toArray();return submissions.map(el => {const $el = $(el);const $next = $el.next();return {rank: $el.find('.rank').text(),title: $el.find('.storylink').text(),link: $el.find('.storylink').attr('href'),score: parseInt($next.find('.score').text(), 10),author: $next.find('.hnuser').text(),time: $next.find('.age').text()};});}
